QuestData.Title: Waygate: Algeth'era
QuestData.Description:
Another stone. Another spire.
Best be gettin' along on yer journey. This one's quite a trek and dangerous tae boot! At least accordin' tae the ones who discovered it.
Are ye up fer it?
QuestData.LogDescription: Locate the Dormant Waygate atop the spire in Algeth'era in Thaldraszus.
